=== 新創作品 ===

與任何重大事件一樣，COVID-19大流行激發了各種流派的許多文化作品的創作。甚至在危機期間，人們都希望會創造出許多新的文化作品，這些作品將直接參考或受到大流行及其影響的啟發。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Dye|first=Josh|url=https://www.smh.com.au/culture/art-and-design/perplexing-and-confusing-art-gallery-of-nsw-director-grapples-with-coronavirus-crisis-20200327-p54emd.html|title='Perplexing and confusing': Art Gallery of NSW director grapples with coronavirus crisis|date=28 March 2020|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|access-date=29 March 2020|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200328225135/https://www.smh.com.au/culture/art-and-design/perplexing-and-confusing-art-gallery-of-nsw-director-grapples-with-coronavirus-crisis-20200327-p54emd.html|archive-date=28 March 2020}}</ref>

